comments: This recording first appeared on a 1976 compilation album, credited to The Crystals on the back cover and to The Ronettes on the disc label. Phil Spector stated that he never recorded the song for The Ronettes, however the lead singer here is clearly Ronnie Spector . The Crystals (actually, La La Brooks + unnamed backing singers and musicians) did record a version of "Girls Can Tell" in late 1963 (first released in 1991).
